================

Cryptos is a work-in-progress repository for software to manipulate 
crypto trading. 

Currently, the only supported platform is KRAKEN.

Usage
------

./kraklib.py --help
usage: kraklib.py [-h] [-d DBFILE] [-s] [-c CANCEL] [-o] [-p]

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -d DBFILE, --dbfile DBFILE
                        DataBase file
  -s, --stats           Show stats
  -c CANCEL, --cancel CANCEL
                        Cancel Order <txid>
  -o, --open            Open Orders
  -p, --place           Place Order


Getting Started
---------------

To run kraklib.py you need to setup a virtual env and install the required packages.

# git clone https://bitbucket.org/ananos/cryptos
# virtualenv -p /usr/bin/python3 ./cryptos
# cd ./cryptos

#### step in the virtual environment
# . ./bin/activate

#### Install krakenex
# ./bin/pip install krakenex

That's it!

You can now check Altcoin statistics:

(krakenlib) # ./kraklib.py -s
COIN    LAST    AVG (DAY)   TOTAL EURO SPENT (DAY)
XXMRZEUR    259.97000000    254.4   ε1m 
XETCZEUR    25.10300000 25.049500000000002  ε1m 
XREPZEUR    30.92900    29.4745 ε444k 
BCHEUR  1452.000000 1460.55 ε7m 
XLTCZEUR    248.01000   231.59499999999997  ε11m 
XETHZEUR    565.74000   536.79  ε20m 
XZECZEUR    388.50900   378.0   ε1m 
XXRPZEUR    0.63200000  0.6334500000000001  ε16m 
XXBTZEUR    14820.00000 14246.0 ε59m 
DASHEUR 741.020000  722.8025    ε1m 

Or check open orders:

(krakenlib) # ./kraklib.py -o
